---
// Site footer — modeled after atlasofurbantech.org
---

<footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-logo">
            <a href="https://tech.cornell.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <img src="/logos/cornell-tech-jacobs.svg" alt="Jacobs Technion-Cornell Institute at Cornell Tech" />
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-description">
            <h3>A Research Project by the Jacobs Urban Tech Hub at Cornell Tech</h3>
            <p>The Urban Tech Hub of the Jacobs Technion-Cornell Institute at Cornell Tech is a new venture in New York City that generates applied research, fosters an expanding tech ecosystem, and cultivates the next generation of leaders in urban technology. Our goal is to shape the field of urban tech with a human-centered approach that focuses first on the people that use the technology. We advance technology research and education to build a better world by increasing access and opportunity within the tech sector.</p>
        </div>

        <nav class="footer-nav">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="https://tech.cornell.edu/programs/masters-programs/jacobs-technion-cornell-dual-ms-urban-tech/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Urban Tech Master's</a>
            <a href="https://urban.tech.cornell.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Urban Tech Hub</a>
            <a href="https://tech.cornell.edu/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cornell Tech</a>
        </nav>
    </div>

</footer>

<style>
    .site-footer {
        background: var(--color-footer);
        color: #eee;
        padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .footer-inner {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        display: flex;
        gap: 2.5rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .footer-logo {
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .footer-logo img {
        height: 120px;
        width: auto;
        display: block;
    }

    .footer-description {
        flex: 1;
    }

    .footer-description h3 {
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .footer-description p {
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #bbb;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .footer-nav {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .footer-nav a {
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .footer-nav a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
        color: var(--color-accent);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .footer-inner {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .footer-nav {
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
        }
    }
</style>
